	(1,'about','index','about','eRentPay: About','eRentPay: About','About','We actually created ERentPay because we ourselves managed our own properties and wanted a service like this to make it easier and less expensive. ','                            <p>We went down many avenues, including hiring property managers, before deciding to create this\n                                service ourselves. We got tired of the high fees, the hassles and the lack of real service.\n                                There was nothing out there to really give a landlord or tenant a break. Are you tired of a\n                                never ending cycle of people with their hands out trying to get your money without actually\n                                earning it? This site puts everything a landlord would need in one place, allowing them to\n                                save their money and use their time more efficiently. But this site does more than that; we\n                                also wanted to give the landlords knowledge. Here there is no bureaucratic wall to keep what\n                                you are missing hidden. You are now free to roam and explore; to effectively manage your\n                                time and money and move on to other things in your lives.</p>\n\n                            <p>When you bought your property you had dreams. There is no reason that you should have to miss\n                                out because the management of your property has become a series of reoccurring problems\n                                begging for your attention. ERentPay is the solution you have been waiting for! Like us, you\n                                now have the ability to pay for only what you need, when you need it, your way. You can\n                                manage your rents, get background and credit checks, create rental contracts along with\n                                receiving online digital signatures, send rental applications, post unit vacancies from the\n                                ERentPay website onto other public sites, and even interact with other landlords and trents,\n                                get background and credit checks, create rental contracts along with receiving online\n                                digital signatures, send rental applications, post unit venants to learn or voice your own\n                                questions and concerns. Explore the horizons and try ERentPay now. You won’t be disappointed\n                                again!</p>',1,1,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(2,'faq','index','faq','eRentPay: FAQ','eRentPay: FAQ','Faq',NULL,'<h3>Is there a monthly fee?</h3>\n\n<p>Yes, when you sign-up there is a monthly recurring fee of $9 charged to the Landlord.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<h3>Do I have to sign a contract?</h3>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>No, there is no long term contract or obligation.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<h3>Can I cancel at any time?</h3>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Yes, you can cancel at any time.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<h3>Are there any hidden fees or obligations?</h3>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>There are other pay-as-you-go fees associated with your account other than the monthly recurring landlord fee and any Transaction fee. These fees are only charged when selected by the Landlord and only as a one-time fee.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<h3>What are the services offered?</h3>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>There are many services, to include; paying rent online, background and credit checks, maintenance request, listing vacant properties online, messaging, communicate with other Landlords and Tenants, create rental contracts and rental applications, allow contracts to be digitally signed online and accounting.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<h3>What if I have any questions?</h3>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Please submit any questions through the contact us page.</p>',1,1,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2015-12-30 10:43:47'),
	(3,'landlord-features','features','landlord-features','eRentPay: Landlord Features','eRentPay: Landlord Features','Landlord Features','Landlord Features','<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n<ul class=\"features-list\"><li><span>Manage your own properties!</span></li>\n	<li><span>Save money on services you will actually need and use, when you need and use them!</span></li>\n	<li><span>Avoid paying a property manager huge fees you can easily use on erentpay yourself!</span></li>\n	<li><span>Completely transparent property management tool allowing landlords to use services as a “pay-as you-go” rather than continual payments for services you may not even need or be using!</span></li>\n	<li><span>No sign-up contract! You can sign-up and pay month to month for as long or briefly as you want with no obligations!</span></li>\n	<li><span>Security is a priority! With erentpay your information and data is safe. We use multiple firewalls, are SSL Certified and PCI Compliance verified secure certification.</span></li>\n	<li><span>Services and monthly fee could be completely free for you as the landlord! To learn more ask our Certified Relator and Property Manager Specialist NOW and start taking back the money you deserve!</span></li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n<h4 class=\"table-title\">Save Big Money with eRentPay!</h4>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"features-table\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-3 features-table-col features-name-col\">\n<ul class=\"table-col-title\"><li class=\"table-overtitle\"> </li>\n	<li class=\"cost-title\"><span>Est. Cost</span></li>\n	<li><span>Background/Credit Checks</span></li>\n	<li><span>Property Listings Online</span></li>\n	<li><span>Rental Applications</span></li>\n	<li><span>Rental Contracts</span></li>\n	<li><span>E-Signature for Applications and Contracts</span></li>\n	<li><span>Maintenance Requests</span></li>\n	<li><span>Accept and Send Payments Online</span></li>\n	<li class=\"tenant-payment\"><s